		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧进行至多3段的4种普通攻击：<br/><span color="#bfffeb">旋-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">挑-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">旋-旋-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">挑-旋</span><span>；每段攻击都造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/>强化版本命中将施加</span><span color="#ccffbf">7</span><span>级「蚀破」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="511" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧从地里挖出雷史莱姆丢出，造成<span color="#ffacff">62.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="422" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧横拿斧子转圈圈，触碰造成<span color="#ffacff">12.5%</span><span>伤害，持续3s，旋转结束后施放尾刀，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/>强化版本命中将施加</span><span color="#ccffbf">7</span><span>级「蚀破」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="511" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧用力将斧子往地上砸，造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，顺势将自己挑起，然后落地坐下，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，雷斧拿着斧子跳起来下落，造成<span color="#df99ff">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>强化版本命中将施加</span><span color="#ccffbf">14</span><span>级「蚀破」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
