		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拟态雷斧将进行一次闪现，显形时立即无视条件施放以下3个技能的随机一个<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>强化版本：「龙卷摧」/「飞象坠」/「斧砍树」。</span></p>
